Intro:
------

!!! PLEASE LEAVE THE COPYRIGHT NOTICE INTACT !!! THANK YOU !!!

Note: Please read the LICENSE file included in the distribution to get the license
      this program is subject to.

phpUseronline is a PHP script that allows you to display User's online
on your website in a very convenient way.

To see this script in action, you can browse the following websites :
- http://www.netone.at
- http://www.erotikbazar.com

Requires:
- PHP v3.x OR v4.x
- mySQL 

Not required but very useful:
- phpMyAdmin would be a very good idea

Changelog:
----------
1.10   	(04/20/2001): 	minor BUG's fixed.

1.00   	(03/09/2001): 	First public release.

Installation:
-------------

- unzip the distribution file into your http documents directory.

- create the mysql database (usually phpUseronline) with mysqladmin.
.) mysqladmin  -u<your_mysql_user> -p<your_mysql_pass> create phpUseronline

- create the mysql tables. you have 2 options :

1) mysql -u<your_mysql_user> -p<your_mysql_pass> phpUseronline<phpUseronline.sql

2) use phpMyAdmin to run the SQL file 'phpUseronline.sql'

- edit the variables in useronline.php to your need's.

